libg15
------------------------------------------
Library to handle the LCD and extra keys on the Logitech G15 Gaming Keyboard
and similar devices

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.1.7-1
  libg15-devel-1.2.9-1bl1
  libg15_1-1.2.9-1bl1
  libusb-devel-1.2.6.0-2
  libusb0-1.2.6.0-2
  pkg-config-1.6.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.35.2-1
  cygport-0.34.0-1
  gcc-core-10.2.0-1
  libtool-2.4.6-7
  make-4.3-1

Canonical website:
  https://gitlab.com/menelkir/libg15

Canonical download:
  https://gitlab.com/menelkir/libg15/-/archive/1.2.9/libg15-1.2.9.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libg15-1.2.9-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libg15-1.2.9-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libg15-1.2.9-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libg15-1.2.9-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libg15_1-1.2.9-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libg15-devel-1.2.9-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libg15)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libg15.README
  /usr/share/doc/libg15/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libg15/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libg15/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libg15/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/libg15/README
  /usr/share/doc/libg15/readme.rst

(libg15_1)
  /usr/bin/cygg15-1.dll

(libg15-devel)
  /usr/include/libg15.h
  /usr/lib/libg15.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libg15.pc

